data.description: Beautiful 2 story home built in 2012 by Ivory Homes homebuilder. This home was the model home in the community. The home has a 2 car garage along with a fully finished basement. Master suite has a master bath and walk-in closet. The home has a brand new backsplash along with the stainless steel microwave and range that have never been used. The home has only been owned by one family and welcomes you and your family!
